The toll gate of the bridge that connects Lekki to the Ikoyi axis of Lagos is currently on Fire. The bridge has been the alternative route for residents since #EndSARS protests went full-blown in the Lekki Toll Gate area.  Video clips seen by SaharaReporters on Tuesday showed all cubicles of the link bridge toll gate burning.  FLASH: Fire Erupts At Lekki Toll Gate#EndSARS #LekkitollgateMassacreFOLLOW LIVE UPDATE: https://t.co/nShvHUMols pic.twitter.com/U5zdIXb83t  The fire outbreak was recorded hours after soldiers opened fire on peaceful #ENDSARS protesters at the Lekki Toll Gate. See Also






